Boardytale licence

You can clone and modify project, run it even for commercial purposes.
That project must have banner with hyperlink to http://www.boardytale.com.
Requested size of banner is min 5% of the first visible frame of branch homepage.
Recommended banners may be in the folder banners in this project.

